      "message": "I see - so the issue is we allocate before validating the size (via readByteArray\u0027s below), which allows for a DOS/OOM style attack.\n\nNote however that textSize is only one of the params which control the allocation size -  glyphCount being the other one.\n\nTo be fully defensive, we should prolly take all these into account and perform a more accurate reader size validation - see below.",
